## Migration to yba_backup_schedule

Replace `yba_backups` with `yba_backup_schedule` and update `keyspace` to `keyspaces` (list):

```hcl
# Before (deprecated)
resource "yba_backups" "example" {
  keyspace = "my_keyspace"
  # ...
}

# After
resource "yba_backup_schedule" "example" {
  keyspaces = ["my_keyspace"]  # Specific keyspace/database
  # ...
}

# Or for full universe backup (all keyspaces/databases):
resource "yba_backup_schedule" "full_backup" {
  keyspaces = []  # Empty list = full universe backup
  # ...
}
```

Then run:
```sh
terraform state mv yba_backups.example yba_backup_schedule.example
```

